coretest

Class ConverterTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • coretest.ConverterTests

  • public class ConverterTests
extends java.lang.Object
    This class converts executes for each given UmlInputRepresentation with its corresponding UmlRepresentationConverter the tests for each of the following converters:
    UmlCodeConverter

    To add a new sample diagram representation to the test suite, the input file has to be added to the resources-folder and the UmlInputRepresentation and UmlRepresentationConverter have to be added to the parameter array in data().
    Author:
    dschoenicke
